Test Cases for Login Page

URL: https://blazedemo.com/login

Test Cases:

1. Verify that the login page has 
a. E-Mail Address Textbox
b. Password Textbox
c. Login Button
d. Remember Me checkbox
e. Login Link
f. Register Link
g. Forgot Your Password? Link
h. BlazeDemo text at top left corner
i. Login at top of the frame

2. Verify that user is not able to login to with blank user name and password, i.e. both fields are mandatory.
3. Verify that cursor is focused on "E-Mail Address" textbox when opening the page.
4. Verify tab functionality: it should move to subsequent values
5. Verify tooltip text is displayed correctly when hovering over E-Mail Address and Password textbox
6. Verify Enter works as substitute of Login Button.
7. Verify minimum and maximum length for the textboxes.
8. Verify Login button functionality
9. Verify user is able to login with valid credentials.
11. Verify Password is in encrypted form.
12. Verify tooltip text if entering invalid E-Mail Address.
13. Verify tooltip text when entering E-Mail address but keeping Password blank and click on Login Button.
14. Verify tooltip text when keeping E-Mail address blank and entering Password value and click on Login Button.
15. Verify clicking on Register link, shows below details to fill:
a. Name Textbox
b. Company Textbox
c. E-Mail Address Textbox
d. Password textbox
e. Confirm Password textbox
f. Register Button
16. Verify clicking on "Forgot Your Password?" Link opens the corresponding page with below fields:
a. E-Mail Address textbox
b. Send Password Reset Link button
17. Verify clicking on "Login" link opens login page.
18. Verify "Remember Me" checkbox is unchecked by default.
19. Verify page source to check if any confidential information is displayed.
20. Verify spaces should not be allowed in password
21. Verify copying the password field value is not allowed and if allowed should not show the password.
22. Verify number of attempts to login
23. Verify complete E-Mail Address is not case sensitive.


